ECB Bond Purchase Program Is ‘Ongoing, Temporary,’ Liikanen Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-09-19T08:50:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/ecb-bond-purchase-program-is-ongoing-temporary-liikanen-says.html
European Central Bank council
member  Erkki Liikanen  said the bank’s Securities Markets Program
is “ongoing, and by character temporary.”  Liikanen, who also heads the Bank of Finland, spoke today
at the Helsinki-based central bank’s press briefing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  